 <i>♪ Tell me, great general,</i>
 <i>what I'm doing is fine ♪</i>

00:10:49.267 --> 00:10:51.901 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>♪ Love should be naked</i>
 <i>so let's watch the world ♪</i>

