 <i>♪ Gone in a flash ♪</i>

00:10:56.634 --> 00:11:00.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>♪ Magic nights I will</i>
 <i>show you an inferno ♪</i>

00:11:00.467 --> 00:11:03.234 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>♪ You will never forget ♪</i>

00:11:06.634 --> 00:11:10.234 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Offers to be on TV</i>
 <i>and radio started pouring in,</i>

00:11:10.267 --> 00:11:11.901 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>She was praised</i>
 <i>for her beauty,</i>

00:11:11.934 --> 00:11:13.834 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>quick wit and skilled speech.</i>

00:11:13.868 --> 00:11:15.167 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>She passed</i>
 <i>the entrance exam</i>

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:17.567 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>to a renowned university</i>
 <i>in a single try</i>

00:11:17.601 --> 00:11:19.200 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>which also made headlines.</i>

00:11:20.167 --> 00:11:21.634 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Looking only at her history,</i>

00:11:21.667 --> 00:11:23.501 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>you could consider</i>
 <i>her life a success,</i>

00:11:23.534 --> 00:11:25.901 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>but she never amounted</i>
 <i>to more than an idol</i>

00:11:25.934 --> 00:11:27.467 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a cult following.</i>

00:11:27.501 --> 00:11:29.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>But her luck also</i>
 <i>brought misfortune.</i>

00:11:29.868 --> 00:11:31.701 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Some held</i>
 <i>a grudge against her.</i>

00:11:31.734 --> 00:11:33.000 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>So we're left to ask:</i>

00:11:33.033 --> 00:11:34.868 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>What were the events that</i>

00:11:34.901 --> 00:11:36.367 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>led to Karin Nanase's</i>
 <i>untimely death</i>

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:39.200 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>and brought the Steel Lady</i>
 <i>into this world?</i>

00:11:42.767 --> 00:11:43.601 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:11:44.767 --> 00:11:46.601 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's a whole site
about her?

00:11:51.767 --> 00:11:52.501 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:11:53.701 --> 00:11:55.868 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>In June of the year</i>
 <i>she turned nineteen,</i>

00:11:55.901 --> 00:11:58.567 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>hen her idol career</i>
 <i>was on the rise,</i>

00:11:58.601 --> 00:11:59.934 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Karin's father died.</i>

00:11:59.968 --> 00:12:02.567 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>He fell down the steps</i>
 <i>to his apartment.</i>

00:12:02.601 --> 00:12:04.067 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>It was ruled an accident,</i>

00:12:04.100 --> 00:12:07.267 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>and nothing about it seemed</i>
 <i>suspicious at the time.</i>

00:12:10.400 --> 00:12:14.167 position:19% line:83% align:start
In honor of my father,
I'm going to keep working hard!

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:17.133 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>However, near the end</i>
 <i>of November that same year,</i>

00:12:17.167 --> 00:12:20.901 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>suspicions suddenly began</i>
 <i>to arise about his death.</i>

00:12:20.934 --> 00:12:22.634 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>There were rumors</i>
 <i>Karin Nanase</i>

00:12:22.667 --> 00:12:23.934 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>resented her father because</i>

00:12:23.968 --> 00:12:25.467 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>he quit work</i>
 <i>when she got famous,</i>

00:12:25.501 --> 00:12:29.100 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>so she killed him and</i>
 <i>made it look like an accident.</i>

00:12:29.133 --> 00:12:31.534 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>There was also a large</i>
 <i>life insurance policy</i>

00:12:31.567 --> 00:12:33.067 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>covering him.</i>

00:12:34.501 --> 00:12:36.834 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Her father had begun</i>
 <i>complaining to his friend</i>

00:12:36.868 --> 00:12:40.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>a month before his fall</i>
 <i>down the stairs.</i>

00:12:40.467 --> 00:12:41.234 position:33% line:89% align:start
[angry grunt]

00:12:41.267 --> 00:12:44.234 position:27% line:83% align:start
That girl's made
a damn fool of me.

00:12:44.267 --> 00:12:48.100 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's always rubbed
how smart she is in my face.

00:12:48.133 --> 00:12:49.501 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Saki] <i>A note hinting</i>
 <i>at his suspicion</i>

00:12:49.534 --> 00:12:51.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>that his daughter</i>
 <i>was trying to kill him</i>

00:12:51.434 --> 00:12:55.267 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>was discovered five months</i>
 <i>after his demise.</i>

00:12:55.300 --> 00:12:57.334 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>That story made</i>
 <i>the rounds online,</i>

00:12:57.367 --> 00:12:59.367 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>and it wasn't long before</i>
 <i>the tabloids and</i>

00:12:59.400 --> 00:13:01.067 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>gossip papers picked it up.</i>

00:13:01.100 --> 00:13:02.501 position:24% line:83% align:start
[agency president]
[angry gasp]

00:13:02.534 --> 00:13:05.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
How dare they publish
this ludicrous article?!

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:08.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
Some other agency must've
spread these rumors.

00:13:08.167 --> 00:13:10.267 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll sue their asses
for libel!

00:13:10.300 --> 00:13:14.000 position:24% line:83% align:start
But sir, a lawsuit,
only exacerbates things.

00:13:14.033 --> 00:13:16.467 position:24% line:83% align:start
The wise move is to
let it quiet down.

00:13:20.133 --> 00:13:22.267 position:24% line:83% align:start
You should go rest
somewhere far away.

00:13:22.300 --> 00:13:23.934 position:30% line:83% align:start
I know you have
what it takes

00:13:23.968 --> 00:13:26.200 position:19% line:83% align:start
to get through a trial
like this.

00:13:26.234 --> 00:13:29.000 position:16% line:83% align:start
You don't need to tell me
what I already know.

00:13:29.033 --> 00:13:30.367 position:13% line:89% align:start
I will be back soon enough,

00:13:30.400 --> 00:13:34.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
so just do your job,
and find me my next one.

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:37.968 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Saki] <i>And so, Karin Nanase</i>
 <i>went on hiatus.</i>

00:13:38.033 --> 00:13:40.133 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Jumping from one hotel</i>
 <i>to another,</i>

00:13:40.167 --> 00:13:42.667 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>staying one step ahead</i>
 <i>of the paparazzi,</i>

00:13:42.701 --> 00:13:44.033 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>In late January,</i>

00:13:44.067 --> 00:13:46.367 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>she found herself</i>
 <i>in Makurazaka City...</i>

00:13:46.400 --> 00:13:50.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>with no idea that</i>
 <i>she'd die a few days later</i>

00:13:50.100 --> 00:13:52.234 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>not far from her hotel.</i>

00:14:07.567 --> 00:14:08.300 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Saki] Detective Terada?

00:14:08.334 --> 00:14:09.367 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:14:09.400 --> 00:14:11.100 position:33% line:83% align:start
Do you think
it's completely unfathomable

00:14:11.133 --> 00:14:13.968 position:19% line:83% align:start
that Steel Lady Nanase
could actually be a ghost?

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:15.367 position:19% line:89% align:start
And here we go again...

00:14:15.400 --> 00:14:17.367 position:24% line:83% align:start
After taking a look
at Nanase's history,

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:20.234 position:13% line:83% align:start
it could make sense for her
to reappear as a ghost.

00:14:20.267 --> 00:14:22.801 position:7% line:83% align:start
Suspicions that she was behind
her father's death

00:14:22.834 --> 00:14:24.100 position:19% line:89% align:start
were never cleared up,

00:14:24.133 --> 00:14:25.734 position:21% line:83% align:start
and those who spread
the rumors

00:14:25.767 --> 00:14:27.234 position:7% line:89% align:start
refused to take responsibility.

00:14:27.267 --> 00:14:29.901 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sure Karin Nanase was
doing whatever she could

00:14:29.934 --> 00:14:31.567 position:13% line:89% align:start
to get her name out there.

00:14:31.601 --> 00:14:32.634 position:27% line:89% align:start
I think I get it,

00:14:32.667 --> 00:14:34.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
how she'd come back
as a vengeful spirit,

00:14:34.868 --> 00:14:37.100 position:19% line:83% align:start
just to attack society
as a whole.

00:14:37.133 --> 00:14:38.567 position:21% line:83% align:start
I think I can believe
that much.

00:14:38.601 --> 00:14:39.801 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, of course,

00:14:39.834 --> 00:14:42.934 position:19% line:83% align:start
I realize the existence
of ghosts seems far-fetched.

00:14:42.968 --> 00:14:44.701 position:16% line:89% align:start
I don't deny they exist.

00:14:44.734 --> 00:14:45.868 position:19% line:89% align:start
Things like spirits...

00:14:45.901 --> 00:14:47.367 position:16% line:83% align:start
I believe in them enough
to go visit

00:14:47.400 --> 00:14:50.033 position:16% line:83% align:start
my relative's gravesites
at least once a year.

00:14:50.067 --> 00:14:52.467 position:38% line:83% align:start
But her?
Something's just different.

00:14:53.701 --> 00:14:55.567 position:33% line:89% align:start
Like she's...

00:14:55.601 --> 00:14:57.200 position:21% line:89% align:start
She seems artificial.

00:14:58.400 --> 00:15:00.834 position:33% line:83% align:start
People saying
she's wearing a mini-skirt

00:15:00.868 --> 00:15:02.634 position:7% line:89% align:start
or is missing part of her face,

00:15:02.667 --> 00:15:04.834 position:13% line:89% align:start
or swinging a steel beam...

00:15:04.868 --> 00:15:07.067 position:21% line:83% align:start
That all just sounds
like stuff

00:15:07.100 --> 00:15:10.200 position:19% line:83% align:start
the society that drove
Karin Nanase to an early death

00:15:10.234 --> 00:15:12.534 position:7% line:89% align:start
would be excited to hear about.

00:15:14.100 --> 00:15:16.501 position:19% line:83% align:start
If she truly came back
to become a vengeful spirit,

00:15:16.534 --> 00:15:19.267 position:21% line:83% align:start
it seems strange that
she'd be dressed that way.

00:15:19.300 --> 00:15:21.501 position:19% line:83% align:start
That means, there must
be something else,

00:15:21.534 --> 00:15:25.901 position:7% line:83% align:start
something hiding in the shadows
other than an idol's will.

00:15:25.934 --> 00:15:27.367 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>He's right.</i>

00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:30.801 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>If the Steel Lady's supposed</i>
 <i>to be a vengeful spirit,</i>

00:15:30.834 --> 00:15:32.234 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>logically, she probably</i>

00:15:32.267 --> 00:15:34.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
wouldn't be pandering
to the masses.

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:37.567 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>But Steel Lady Nanase</i>
 <i>is a vengeful spirit,</i>

00:15:37.601 --> 00:15:40.267 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>but sadly, at this point,</i>
 <i>it's nearly impossible</i>

00:15:40.300 --> 00:15:42.667 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>to convince</i>
 <i>Detective Terada of that.</i>

00:15:42.701 --> 00:15:44.033 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's not all...

00:15:44.067 --> 00:15:47.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
The possibility does exist
that her accidental death

00:15:47.200 --> 00:15:48.801 position:27% line:83% align:start
may have actually
been a murder and

00:15:48.834 --> 00:15:50.100 position:24% line:89% align:start
that's what caused

00:15:50.133 --> 00:15:52.534 position:21% line:83% align:start
the Steel Lady Nanase
incidents to begin.

00:15:52.567 --> 00:15:55.000 position:13% line:89% align:start
Ah! Right. Yes, of course.

00:15:55.033 --> 00:15:56.968 position:13% line:89% align:start
The investigation files...

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:58.367 position:13% line:83% align:start
If you'd look through them
for me,

00:15:58.400 --> 00:16:00.834 position:7% line:83% align:start
and just explain the important
parts to me later.

00:16:00.868 --> 00:16:02.467 position:35% line:83% align:start
That would
be extremely helpful.

00:16:02.501 --> 00:16:03.133 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:16:04.200 --> 00:16:06.968 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Kotoko] <i>I'm completely</i>
 <i>lost about what to do...</i>

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:09.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Normally, I'd be able to</i>
 <i>just talk to the ghosts,</i>

00:16:09.968 --> 00:16:11.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>even if they didn't</i>
 <i>have a face,</i>

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:12.868 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>we could still communicate.</i>

00:16:12.901 --> 00:16:14.300 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>It goes without saying,</i>

00:16:14.334 --> 00:16:16.400 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>those who are powerful</i>
 <i>enough to kill people,</i>

00:16:16.434 --> 00:16:19.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>have to possess a certain</i>
 <i>amount of intelligence.</i>

00:16:19.133 --> 00:16:21.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>But that's not the case</i>
 <i>with Steel Lady Nanase.</i>

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:23.934 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>She's supposed to be a ghost,</i>

00:16:23.968 --> 00:16:26.300 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>but I sensed no will</i>
 <i>or ability to think,</i>

00:16:26.334 --> 00:16:28.534 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and she didn't respond</i>
 <i>to my voice.</i>

00:16:28.567 --> 00:16:31.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>A grudge, evil thoughts,</i>
 <i>vindictive feelings...</i>

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:33.901 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Those should power</i>
 <i>her existence,</i>

00:16:33.934 --> 00:16:36.334 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>but I don't sense them</i>
 <i>in her, either.</i>

00:16:36.367 --> 00:16:39.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's almost as if</i>
 <i>she's an empty puppet...</i>

00:16:40.300 --> 00:16:42.934 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Her very existence is</i>
 <i>enough to terrify</i>

00:16:42.968 --> 00:16:45.000 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>all of the yokai</i>
 <i>in Makurazaka City</i>

00:16:45.033 --> 00:16:46.534 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>out of ever going near her.</i>

00:16:46.567 --> 00:16:50.434 position:7% line:83% align:start
I really wish I had more useful
information to work with...

00:16:52.801 --> 00:16:54.968 position:19% line:83% align:start
This illustration looks
exactly like

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:56.868 position:10% line:89% align:start
what I encountered yesterday.

00:16:56.901 --> 00:16:58.367 position:10% line:89% align:start
Between all the eyewitnesses,

00:16:58.400 --> 00:17:01.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
and knowing what the living
Karin Nanase looked like,

00:17:01.133 --> 00:17:03.300 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm sure something similar
could be drawn,

00:17:03.334 --> 00:17:07.133 position:21% line:83% align:start
but is it possible to
draw something this accurate?

00:17:07.167 --> 00:17:09.000 position:19% line:83% align:start
This illustration looks
like it was done

00:17:09.033 --> 00:17:12.234 position:24% line:83% align:start
by someone who saw
Steel Lady Nanase personally.

00:17:13.868 --> 00:17:15.033 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:17:15.067 --> 00:17:17.467 position:38% line:83% align:start
Except...
It's actually the opposite.

00:17:17.501 --> 00:17:18.701 position:30% line:89% align:start
If that's true,

00:17:18.734 --> 00:17:21.934 position:21% line:83% align:start
it's going to be much
more difficult to defeat her.

00:17:21.968 --> 00:17:25.000 position:21% line:83% align:start
First thing's first,
I need more info.

00:17:25.033 --> 00:17:26.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
All the information
they have online

00:17:26.868 --> 00:17:28.701 position:24% line:89% align:start
is a jumbled mess.

00:17:28.734 --> 00:17:30.300 position:13% line:89% align:start
I want accurate references,

00:17:30.334 --> 00:17:32.634 position:21% line:83% align:start
everything regarding
Karin Nanase's death

00:17:32.667 --> 00:17:33.868 position:19% line:89% align:start
from a reliable source.

00:17:33.901 --> 00:17:36.634 position:19% line:89% align:start
Which means the police.

00:17:36.667 --> 00:17:37.968 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:41.367 position:16% line:83% align:start
The last thing I want is
to ask Saki for a favor!

00:17:43.200 --> 00:17:45.167 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The body of Karin Nanase</i>
 <i>was found</i>

00:17:45.200 --> 00:17:47.934 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>on Saturday January 30th.</i>

00:17:47.968 --> 00:17:49.767 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>The location was</i>
 <i>a construction site</i>

00:17:49.801 --> 00:17:51.367 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>that was near her hotel.</i>

00:17:52.467 --> 00:17:54.968 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>She was found by</i>
 <i>an old man who lived</i>

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:56.601 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>between the hotel</i>
 <i>she was staying at</i>

00:17:56.634 --> 00:17:58.033 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and the construction site.</i>

00:17:58.067 --> 00:18:00.601 position:10% line:83% align:start
The night before I discovered
the young lady's body,

00:18:00.634 --> 00:18:04.334 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought I heard something
like a steel beam falling.

00:18:04.367 --> 00:18:07.100 position:21% line:83% align:start
It was really raining
hard that day,

00:18:07.133 --> 00:18:09.734 position:24% line:83% align:start
So, I thought that
might've caused something

00:18:09.767 --> 00:18:10.934 position:30% line:89% align:start
to fall apart.

00:18:10.968 --> 00:18:13.300 position:30% line:83% align:start
I went to check
the next morning.

00:18:14.767 --> 00:18:15.367 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:18:16.501 --> 00:18:20.300 position:27% line:83% align:start
And as I figured,
some steel beams had fallen.

00:18:25.400 --> 00:18:28.367 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Saki] <i>The steel beam</i>
 <i>that had killed her</i>

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:31.067 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>was about three</i>
 <i>to five meters long,</i>

00:18:31.100 --> 00:18:33.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the body's face and</i>
 <i>head had been shattered.</i>

00:18:34.000 --> 00:18:36.067 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Her face was unrecognizable,</i>

00:18:36.100 --> 00:18:38.133 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and dental records</i>
 <i>wouldn't help.</i>

00:18:38.167 --> 00:18:41.033 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Everything was crushed</i>
 <i>from the neck up.</i>

00:18:41.067 --> 00:18:43.634 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>The police found</i>
 <i>her cell phone, wallet,</i>

00:18:43.667 --> 00:18:45.167 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>and university ID,</i>

00:18:45.200 --> 00:18:48.334 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>which led them to believe</i>
 <i>that it was Haruko Nanase.</i>

00:18:48.367 --> 00:18:50.033 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Her fingerprints</i>
 <i>from the hotel room</i>

00:18:50.067 --> 00:18:52.467 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>matched those on</i>
 <i>her personal belongings,</i>

00:18:52.501 --> 00:18:56.234 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>they declared the body was,</i>
 <i>in fact, Karin Nanase's.</i>

00:18:56.267 --> 00:18:58.267 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>The estimated</i>
 <i>time of death was</i>

00:18:58.300 --> 00:19:00.901 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>between midnight</i>
 <i>and 1 a.m. on the 30th.</i>

00:19:00.934 --> 00:19:05.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Which also matches the time</i>
 <i>the old man heard the noise.</i>

00:19:05.133 --> 00:19:07.501 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>The police continued</i>
 <i>their investigation</i>

00:19:07.534 --> 00:19:08.567 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>with the possibilities</i>

00:19:08.601 --> 00:19:11.167 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>of an accident,</i>
 <i>murder, or suicide.</i>

00:19:11.200 --> 00:19:14.367 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>But officially,</i>
 <i>it was ruled an accident.</i>

00:19:14.400 --> 00:19:15.634 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Normally,</i>

00:19:15.667 --> 00:19:18.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>they would've come</i>
 <i>to a conclusion much faster...</i>

00:19:18.868 --> 00:19:20.234 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Perhaps it's because</i>

00:19:20.267 --> 00:19:22.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>this was the bizarre death</i>
 <i>of an idol,</i>

00:19:22.133 --> 00:19:23.968 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>but they're taking</i>
 <i>their time and</i>

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:27.067 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>putting a lot of work</i>
 <i>into the investigation.</i>

00:19:27.100 --> 00:19:28.734 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Probably because</i>
 <i>the department's reputation</i>

00:19:28.767 --> 00:19:30.400 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>is on the line.</i>

00:19:30.434 --> 00:19:34.100 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>But there's one part,</i>
 <i>one thing that's bugging me.</i>

00:19:34.133 --> 00:19:39.033 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Karin's older sister</i>
 <i>and the statement she made.</i>

00:19:39.067 --> 00:19:40.667 position:38% line:83% align:start
- <i>She...</i>
-[sudden knock]

00:19:40.701 --> 00:19:42.133 position:35% line:89% align:start
[surprise]

00:19:43.467 --> 00:19:44.267 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:19:46.734 --> 00:19:47.567 position:41% line:89% align:start
[fear]

