00:19:50.501 --> 00:19:51.501 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Saki startled]

00:20:03.467 --> 00:20:05.200 position:30% line:89% align:start
[yokai] [snarl]

00:20:08.868 --> 00:20:10.501 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:20:10.534 --> 00:20:12.667 position:24% line:89% align:start
[in pain/startled]

00:20:12.701 --> 00:20:14.400 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:20:14.434 --> 00:20:15.300 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Saki] Yokai?

00:20:18.601 --> 00:20:19.601 position:33% line:89% align:start
Saki scared]

00:20:21.868 --> 00:20:25.133 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Gen'ichiro] I'm terribly sorry
to disturb you so late!

00:20:25.167 --> 00:20:27.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
Ugh! I cannot blame
your ladyship

00:20:27.868 --> 00:20:29.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
for being surprised
by my visit!

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.067 position:35% line:83% align:start
Allow me to
introduce myself!

00:20:31.100 --> 00:20:33.100 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm the Tree Spirit
known as Gen'ichiro!

00:20:33.133 --> 00:20:34.467 position:35% line:83% align:start
I have come
before you tonight

00:20:34.501 --> 00:20:38.234 position:19% line:83% align:start
on orders from our lady
of one eye and one leg!

00:20:38.267 --> 00:20:41.968 position:35% line:83% align:start
Our lady of
one eye and one leg?

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:43.767 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>It must be her!</i>

00:20:43.801 --> 00:20:44.567 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Kotoko] <i>Yay!</i>

00:20:44.601 --> 00:20:45.767 position:33% line:89% align:start
I beg of you!

00:20:45.801 --> 00:20:47.100 position:33% line:83% align:start
Please do not
be violent with me.

00:20:47.133 --> 00:20:49.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
I come to you in peace!
And besides,

00:20:49.300 --> 00:20:51.767 position:19% line:83% align:start
I am nothing more than
an old and frail tree spirit!

00:20:51.801 --> 00:20:53.067 position:33% line:89% align:start
Please stop.

00:20:53.100 --> 00:20:55.300 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's no reason for
a spirit to fear me.

00:20:55.334 --> 00:20:57.701 position:21% line:83% align:start
And could you please
keep it down?

00:20:57.734 --> 00:20:58.601 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:20:58.634 --> 00:21:00.000 position:24% line:89% align:start
But my lady told me

00:21:00.033 --> 00:21:02.133 position:24% line:83% align:start
that you had rather
