00:21:02.167 --> 00:21:04.634 position:10% line:83% align:start
And that I should be careful,
and mind my manners...

00:21:04.667 --> 00:21:07.300 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm punching that brat</i>
 <i>the next time I see her...</i>

00:21:07.334 --> 00:21:10.868 position:24% line:83% align:start
Okay. So, what does
she want with me?

00:21:10.901 --> 00:21:12.133 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's in regards

00:21:12.167 --> 00:21:14.334 position:27% line:83% align:start
to the Steel Lady
Nanase situation.

00:21:14.367 --> 00:21:17.400 position:21% line:83% align:start
