request your assistance

00:21:17.434 --> 00:21:18.434 position:30% line:89% align:start
in the matter.

00:21:18.467 --> 00:21:19.601 position:24% line:89% align:start
She needs my help?

00:21:19.634 --> 00:21:21.734 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Gen'ichiro] If you cannot
offer any assistance,

00:21:21.767 --> 00:21:23.100 position:27% line:89% align:start
then from now on,

00:21:23.133 --> 00:21:25.968 position:19% line:83% align:start
prepare for every night
to be just like this...

00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.801 position:13% line:89% align:start
The tree spirits Gen'jiro,

00:21:27.834 --> 00:21:29.868 position:19% line:83% align:start
Gen'zaburo, Gen'shiro,
and so on

00:21:29.901 --> 00:21:31.601 position:27% line:83% align:start
will come asking
for your assistance,

00:21:31.634 --> 00:21:32.968 position:19% line:89% align:start
just as I have tonight.

00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:34.434 position:13% line:89% align:start
How many of you are there?

00:21:34.467 --> 00:21:36.834 position:27% line:83% align:start
This is basically
just bullying me!

00:21:36.868 --> 00:21:38.667 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, according to my lady,

00:21:38.701 --> 00:21:41.167 position:10% line:83% align:start
