there is to know

00:21:41.200 --> 00:21:42.968 position:30% line:83% align:start
about the life
and especially,

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:44.767 position:33% line:83% align:start
the death of
the human entertainer

00:21:44.801 --> 00:21:46.534 position:19% line:89% align:start
known as Karin Nanase,

00:21:46.567 --> 00:21:47.701 position:21% line:89% align:start
So she can figure out

00:21:47.734 --> 00:21:49.968 position:33% line:83% align:start
how to defeat
Steel Lady Nanase.

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:51.434 position:35% line:83% align:start
As for why
she wanted to know,

00:21:51.467 --> 00:21:54.267 position:13% line:83% align:start
