and tell you herself.

00:21:55.434 --> 00:21:57.868 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>She's also wondering</i>
 <i>about what lead</i>

00:21:57.901 --> 00:21:59.901 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>to Karin Nanase death?</i>

00:21:59.934 --> 00:22:03.067 position:27% line:83% align:start
All right, then.
Where do I go?

00:22:04.000 --> 00:22:05.901 position:35% line:83% align:start
[waitress]
Thank you for waiting.

00:22:05.934 --> 00:22:08.100 position:10% line:89% align:start
Here's your seafood yakisoba.

00:22:09.167 --> 00:22:12.701 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I wonder if Saki</i>
 <i>will actually show up.</i>

00:22:12.734 --> 00:22:15.033 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even if she were</i>
 <i>to help me out,</i>

00:22:15.067 --> 00:22:16.667 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I wonder if she'll</i>
 <i>be able</i>

00:22:16.701 --> 00:22:18.300 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>to provide me with any files.</i>

00:22:20.734 --> 00:22:22.200 position:30% line:89% align:start
Not bad at all.

00:22:23.133 --> 00:22:24.667 position:19% line:83% align:start
[grade-schooler ghost]
My lady?

00:22:24.701 --> 00:22:24.734 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:22:25.934 --> 00:22:28.567 position:27% line:83% align:start
Steel Lady Nanase
just showed up.

00:22:28.601 --> 00:22:29.734 position:38% line:89% align:start
Where at?

00:22:29.767 --> 00:22:32.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
The 3-chome bus stop
in Makurazaka.

00:22:32.501 --> 00:22:33.467 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>She's close.</i>

00:22:34.467 --> 00:22:35.501 position:21% line:89% align:start
