she gives it a little time.

00:22:42.567 --> 00:22:43.367 position:44% line:89% align:start
'kay.

00:22:44.100 --> 00:22:46.567 position:7% line:89% align:start
And Saki just adores children.

00:22:46.601 --> 00:22:48.734 position:13% line:89% align:start
