get attacked.

00:23:01.133 --> 00:23:03.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's impossible for me to
try covering the whole city,

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:05.901 position:38% line:83% align:start
but since
she appeared close by,

00:23:05.934 --> 00:23:07.067 position:19% line:89% align:start
I need to do something.

00:23:07.100 --> 00:23:09.167 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[metal tapping]
-[growl]

00:23:10.467 --> 00:23:12.000 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's her!</i>

00:23:15.734 --> 00:23:18.367 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>Oh no...</i>
 <i>She's attacking someone.</i>

00:23:20.567 --> 00:23:23.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:23:25.868 --> 00:23:27.534 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:23:28.267 --> 00:23:30.501 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Kuro grunts and groans]

00:23:31.501 --> 00:23:32.467 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:23:34.868 --> 00:23:36.601 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

00:23:38.534 --> 00:23:39.601 position:41% line:89% align:start
[fear]

00:23:43.968 --> 00:23:45.467 position:30% line:89% align:start
Is that Kuro?!

00:23:53.100 --> 00:23:54.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Kuro Sakuragawa is</i>
 <i>having trouble</i>

00:23:54.868 --> 00:23:57.033 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>with Steel Lady Nanase's</i>
 <i>fierce attacks.</i>

00:23:57.067 --> 00:23:58.501 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>She is no normal spectre.</i>

00:23:58.534 --> 00:24:01.267 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>After Karin Nanase's death,</i>
 <i>why did she manifest</i>

00:24:01.300 --> 00:24:03.601 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>as a monster and</i>
 <i>gain such powers?</i>

00:24:03.634 --> 00:24:04.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Next time,</i>

